				<outline text="So heartbreaking what long haulers have had to endure while our system fails them in nearly every way. This is a powerful piece by @morganstephensa &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.cnn.com/2021/07/23/opinions/long-covid-symptoms-brought-me-to-the-brink-stephens/index.html&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Mon, 26 Jul 2021 13:53:16 GMT" tweetId="1419657073499906054" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1419657073499906054" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" >
