			<outline text="July 25" type="calendarDay" name="25" >
				<outline text="Yes baby, come to mama &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/tmz/status/1419297395238588423&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Mon, 26 Jul 2021 02:04:35 GMT" tweetId="1419478724416741379" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1419478724416741379" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
				<outline text="Declining air quality is so devastating for those with underlying health conditions. I had a really hard time too in LA last fall 💔 &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/steven_aquino/status/1419461064207396865&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Mon, 26 Jul 2021 00:57:24 GMT" tweetId="1419461816527241218" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1419461816527241218" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
				<outline text="“Smoke fallout could very well be the West’s — and then the country’s — next health epidemic. Air quality experts are still trying to wrap their heads around this crisis.” Excellent piece by @cwarzel &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.nytimes.com/2021/07/25/opinion/west-coast-fires-smoke.html&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Mon, 26 Jul 2021 00:44:44 GMT" tweetId="1419458631641174017" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1419458631641174017" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" >
					<outline text="Poor air quality threatens our health in so many ways, some we’re only just beginning to understand &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.nytimes.com/2021/07/25/opinion/west-coast-fires-smoke.html&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt; https://t.co/neT2F0xgHc" type="tweet" created="Mon, 26 Jul 2021 00:48:59 GMT" tweetId="1419459701448736768" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1419459701448736768" inReplyToId="1419458631641174017" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" >
						<outline text="This is also a must read and made me sad to think how much Colorado has also changed in the past 20 years alone &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.nytimes.com/2021/07/22/opinion/yosemite-west-coast-smoke.html&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Mon, 26 Jul 2021 00:55:22 GMT" tweetId="1419461307015733248" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1419461307015733248" inReplyToId="1419459701448736768" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
						</outline>
