				<outline text="All press is good press 😅 &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/stephemcneal/status/1418151149149081605&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Thu, 22 Jul 2021 20:06:20 GMT" tweetId="1418301407304708096" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1418301407304708096" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
				<outline text=".@BKCHarvard is launching an Institute for Rebooting Social Media, a three-year research initiative to address social media’s most urgent problems, including misinformation, privacy breaches, harassment, and content governance. &lt;a href=&quot;https://cyber.harvard.edu/story/2021-07/note-jonathan-zittrain-exciting-news-opportunities-bkc&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Thu, 22 Jul 2021 19:37:30 GMT" tweetId="1418294151334928385" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1418294151334928385" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" >
					<outline text="@BKCHarvard &quot;Platforms initially perceived as engines for democracy and truth-telling appear to have instead facilitated the spread and acceptance of lies, division, and physical harm.&quot; 
&lt;a href=&quot;https://cyber.harvard.edu/story/2021-07/berkman-klein-center-to-launch-three-year-institute-for-rebooting-social-media&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Thu, 22 Jul 2021 19:47:10 GMT" tweetId="1418296580495450112" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1418296580495450112" inReplyToId="1418294151334928385" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
					</outline>
				<outline text="&quot;Survivors of trauma, including sexual assault, deserve the full support of their newsrooms. They should never have to fear that they will be punished, silenced or barred from doing their jobs because of what was done to them,&quot; @feliciasonmez &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.cnn.com/2021/07/22/media/washington-post-lawsuit-felicia-sonmez/index.html&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Thu, 22 Jul 2021 16:52:44 GMT" tweetId="1418252683601874947" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1418252683601874947" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
				<outline text="!!!!!!!!! have never clicked play faster on a pod &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/4evrmalone/status/1417848319997628425&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Thu, 22 Jul 2021 16:51:02 GMT" tweetId="1418252256328122368" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1418252256328122368" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
				<outline text="“As chronically ill people, we are always attempting to make ourselves more manageable, to be around other people in a way that’s more comfortable for them. And home for me is the place where I don’t have to do any of that.” &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.apartmenttherapy.com/how-chronically-ill-people-make-home-comfortable-36950267&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Thu, 22 Jul 2021 04:23:48 GMT" tweetId="1418064209254834179" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1418064209254834179" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
