			<outline text="July 21" type="calendarDay" name="21" >
				<outline text="Seeing ppl praise this piece on Covid breakthrough risk, but seems like an oversight to make 0 mention of long Covid. The risk of long Covid in even mild cases is something that should be at least talked abt. It’s horrific/debilitating for those who suffer &lt;a href=&quot;https://slate.com/technology/2021/07/covid-delta-variant-risk-vaccinated-breakthrough-cases.html&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Wed, 21 Jul 2021 22:30:33 GMT" tweetId="1417975312919318528" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1417975312919318528" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
