				<outline text="&quot;Vaccinated people: Your odds of a COVID 'breakthrough' infection have gone up. That doesn't mean you need to panic.&quot; Hope everyone reading this stays safe, even a mild case of covid can lead to debilitating #longcovid symptoms &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.businessinsider.com/fully-vaccinated-people-not-immune-to-covid-milder-2021-7&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Tue, 20 Jul 2021 15:34:22 GMT" tweetId="1417508188228784128" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1417508188228784128" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" >
					<outline text="“One thing that was surprising to us was the large percentage of asymptomatic patients that are in that category of #longcovid… Some of these manifestations are chronic conditions that will last a lifetime and will forever scar some individuals” &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.nytimes.com/2021/06/15/health/covid-19-patients.html&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Tue, 20 Jul 2021 16:01:54 GMT" tweetId="1417515117655117827" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1417515117655117827" inReplyToId="1417508188228784128" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
