			<outline text="July 19" type="calendarDay" name="19" >
				<outline text="Really important story that shows how too often white cis men are the only ones considered “objective” by media bosses. &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/npr/status/1416775123068194823&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Tue, 20 Jul 2021 02:56:27 GMT" tweetId="1417317453143560192" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1417317453143560192" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
				<outline text="Jealous of this story &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/nymag/status/1417311882063622145&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Tue, 20 Jul 2021 02:39:19 GMT" tweetId="1417313137854803968" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1417313137854803968" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
				<outline text="How bad would it be to just stream off my 2018 MacBook if I’m not gaming? Like, if I’m just streaming a just chatting would that fry my comp? My streamer friends are trying to shame me into getting a whole ass gaming computer 🤨" type="tweet" created="Tue, 20 Jul 2021 02:00:33 GMT" tweetId="1417303383111733277" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1417303383111733277" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" >
					<outline text="Love all the earnest responses of “expense it to NYT!” as if the company is gonna be totally fine financing my personal hobby gamer pivot" type="tweet" created="Tue, 20 Jul 2021 05:26:50 GMT" tweetId="1417355298017202185" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1417355298017202185" inReplyToId="1417303383111733277" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
					</outline>
				<outline text="This is ultimately why I quit freelance life (and healthcare costs!) &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/kantrowitz/status/1417204671664443397&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Tue, 20 Jul 2021 01:51:52 GMT" tweetId="1417301200031027227" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1417301200031027227" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
				<outline text="Great interview with @edzitron who has become one of the most prescient media critics and great blogger of our times &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/bradesposito/status/1417270991781208071&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Tue, 20 Jul 2021 01:50:01 GMT" tweetId="1417300734656221191" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1417300734656221191" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
				<outline text="“By no means at all is gaming a niche thing anymore. It’s gonna continue to just eat everything else because it’s the most engaging and the most technologically cutting edge of all entertainment forms.” &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.washingtonpost.com/video-games/2021/07/12/video-game-fashion-esports-streetwear/&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt; by @JordanOloman" type="tweet" created="Tue, 20 Jul 2021 01:39:48 GMT" tweetId="1417298163224903682" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1417298163224903682" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
				<outline text="RIP @GilmerHealthLaw 💔 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.nytimes.com/2021/07/17/health/erin-gilmer-dead.html&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Mon, 19 Jul 2021 22:28:02 GMT" tweetId="1417249903781179399" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1417249903781179399" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
				<outline text="I wish there was someone who could do my expenses for me for a fee it's the worst part of having a job, I can't believe I used to do it for 9 hours a day as an admin" type="tweet" created="Mon, 19 Jul 2021 21:55:41 GMT" tweetId="1417241762037305382" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1417241762037305382" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" >
					<outline text="it's called workday b/c it takes an entire workday to do one thing 😌 &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/benlikestocode/status/1417245135268683776&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Mon, 19 Jul 2021 22:13:09 GMT" tweetId="1417246155495272516" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1417246155495272516" inReplyToId="1417241762037305382" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
					</outline>
				<outline text="Rhett And Link Are YouTube Legends. Now They Want To Be Investors, Too &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.forbes.com/sites/abrambrown/2021/07/19/rhett-link-youtube-fund-creator-economy-investment-mythical-entertainment/&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Mon, 19 Jul 2021 21:45:51 GMT" tweetId="1417239287486025730" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1417239287486025730" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
				<outline text="It’s really scary how cavalier some friends have gotten lately about getting post vaxx Covid. You can still become potentially permanently disabled after a mild infection due to #longcovid. Anyone dealing w/ chronic health issues caused by Covid know it’s no joke. Pls stay safe🙏🏻" type="tweet" created="Mon, 19 Jul 2021 20:59:27 GMT" tweetId="1417227607481847819" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1417227607481847819" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
				<outline text="Really damning account of corporate culture inside WeWork in @eliotwb’s THE CULT OF WE. 

Adam Neumann apparently sought to leak unflattering photos of a former employee in an effort to discredit her sexual harassment claims &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.cultofwe.com/&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt; https://t.co/4Gi637pzK1" type="tweet" created="Mon, 19 Jul 2021 19:35:03 GMT" tweetId="1417206369917161481" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1417206369917161481" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
				<outline text="If you see any influencers promoting either getting vaccinated (or anti vaxx messaging), DM me the links to their content please!! 🙏🏻" type="tweet" created="Mon, 19 Jul 2021 18:48:05 GMT" tweetId="1417194550112636931" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1417194550112636931" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
				</outline>
