					<outline text="The irony of this footage being captured by Nelk, who literally rode on Air Force One with Trump last year but of course didn't face a fraction of this backlash" type="tweet" created="Fri, 16 Jul 2021 19:39:43 GMT" tweetId="1416120378171305985" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1416120378171305985" inReplyToId="1416120072679084037" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
