				<outline text="A peek into @xpatriciah's internet &lt;a href=&quot;https://embedded.substack.com/p/my-internet-patricia-hernandez&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Fri, 16 Jul 2021 17:15:49 GMT" tweetId="1416084167784271879" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1416084167784271879" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
				<outline text="“Our system is called capitalism. It’s designed to optimize for long-term growth of capital. When people wonder, ‘Well, are capital owners advantaged over labor?,’ it ain’t called laborism.” &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.nytimes.com/2021/07/16/style/uber-ceo-dara-khosrowshahi.html&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Fri, 16 Jul 2021 17:12:40 GMT" tweetId="1416083374834323463" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1416083374834323463" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
