			<outline text="July 15" type="calendarDay" name="15" >
				<outline text="These stories of #longcovid are horrifying. I hope those suffering get the treatment and acknowledgment they deserve. Scary how dismissive our systems can be to those who are disabled or suffer w/ chronic illness &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-scotland-57693637&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Fri, 16 Jul 2021 03:15:05 GMT" tweetId="1415872590095204353" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1415872590095204353" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
				<outline text="My child &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/adet0la/status/1415770805452120067&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Fri, 16 Jul 2021 02:45:52 GMT" tweetId="1415865238210158592" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1415865238210158592" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
				<outline text="Buried scoop: Virgil Abloh is building a virtual clothing brand for clothes to wear in the metaverse. 

&quot;I want to make virtual clothes to paint pictures physical clothes cannot, and let buyers access a new dimension of their personal style&quot; Mr. Abloh said &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.matthewball.vc/all/csametaverse&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Thu, 15 Jul 2021 20:53:42 GMT" tweetId="1415776611580928006" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1415776611580928006" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" >
					<outline text="Abloh has been really into NFTs, back in February he said, &quot;the real world is just the part-time metaverse.&quot; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.instagram.com/p/CLwtSDEpsBO/&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Thu, 15 Jul 2021 20:55:35 GMT" tweetId="1415777086283862022" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1415777086283862022" inReplyToId="1415776611580928006" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
					</outline>
				<outline text="Sounds about right &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/MikaelThalen/status/1415764784067186688&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Thu, 15 Jul 2021 20:31:10 GMT" tweetId="1415770939799842821" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1415770939799842821" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
				<outline text="&quot;The notion of a special bond with a creator is contrived, and what seems like unfettered access to their lives is curated. It’s the intimacy you’d get from any imaginary friend.&quot; Fantastic piece by @fadeke_adegbuyi on parasocial relationships &lt;a href=&quot;https://every.to/cybernaut/the-blurred-lines-of-parasocial-relationships&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Thu, 15 Jul 2021 20:29:41 GMT" tweetId="1415770566242545667" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1415770566242545667" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
				<outline text="This is how we win 🔥 &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/criterion/status/1415710012442296324&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Thu, 15 Jul 2021 17:15:07 GMT" tweetId="1415721603007197186" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1415721603007197186" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
				<outline text="A thread by the co-creator of dogecoin. Interested to hear people's thoughts here &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/ummjackson/status/1415353984617914370&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Thu, 15 Jul 2021 16:01:25 GMT" tweetId="1415703053555150849" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1415703053555150849" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" >
					<outline text="Found this thread very interesting &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/evan_greer/status/1415640716357906433&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Thu, 15 Jul 2021 22:59:38 GMT" tweetId="1415808300936044544" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1415808300936044544" inReplyToId="1415703053555150849" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
					</outline>
				<outline text=".@NoahShachtman is intense and fearless and I will always be indebted to him for giving me my first full time reporting job. Respect to him always and congrats on the new gig, everyone at Rolling Stone is very lucky 🔥&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.nytimes.com/2021/07/15/business/rolling-stone-new-editor.html&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Thu, 15 Jul 2021 15:40:26 GMT" tweetId="1415697773425483777" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1415697773425483777" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
				<outline text="Middle-aged mums &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.dailymail.co.uk/sciencetech/article-9786635/Middle-aged-MUMS-likely-troll-social-media-influencers.html&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Thu, 15 Jul 2021 15:20:04 GMT" tweetId="1415692648422285312" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1415692648422285312" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
				<outline text="The whole &quot;leaving SF&quot; thing was just about the RTs for so many ppl &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.nytimes.com/2021/07/15/technology/tech-workers-bay-area-back.html&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Thu, 15 Jul 2021 15:08:21 GMT" tweetId="1415689700233318404" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1415689700233318404" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
