					<outline text="For those just learning about Olivia Rodrigo definitley check out @joecoscarelli's great Diary of a Song w/ her! &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.nytimes.com/2021/02/26/arts/music/olivia-rodrigo-drivers-license.html&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Tue, 13 Jul 2021 16:01:27 GMT" tweetId="1414978286904619013" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1414978286904619013" inReplyToId="1414977014101168130" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
