				<outline text="FYI: Tons of young influencers have been doing videos with Fauci and creating content w/ the White House encouraging people to get vaccinated. Tinx did one recently too! &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/jeneps/status/1414962370783363074&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Tue, 13 Jul 2021 15:55:33 GMT" tweetId="1414976801277894659" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1414976801277894659" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
				<outline text="I spy @joshgondelman @jerm_cohen  the Green Lady and more on this @brooklynmag list of the 50 most fascinating people in Brooklyn &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.bkmag.com/brooklyns-50-most-fascinating/&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Tue, 13 Jul 2021 15:35:02 GMT" tweetId="1414971639096348684" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1414971639096348684" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
