				<outline text="So impressed with @theinformation @kyurieff really useful Creator Economy startup database. I'm sure they'll be adding lots more as this sector continue to boom https://t.co/6DVeMk8vOo" type="tweet" created="Mon, 28 Jun 2021 20:01:19 GMT" tweetId="1409602833968635911" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1409602833968635911" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" >
