You can donate to make us drop our weapons and basically ruin our chances of winning. Donate/watch: https://t.co/PZH8QhwxnF https://t.co/yeXftxnHlN" type="tweet" created="Sun, 27 Jun 2021 20:50:28 GMT" tweetId="1409252817479499783" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1409252817479499783" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
